snippet.title: Arcade Game: Two Tigers (1984 Bally Midway)
snippet.description:
A shooting 'em up game where you shoot down as many planes to down the ship. The game starts tell you how many ships you must sink.  Others may assisted if you shoot them down as well. The game continues until you fail to sink 2 ships.

Gameplay starts at 2:37

Note: Used invincibility and infinite time cheat when close on running out of time. The game is endless so I quit afterwards.
